uster E+A galaxy and enforces the notion that these objects are the\nresult of a recent rejuvenation episode rather than a genuine delayed\nformation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Oct 2006 11:50:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
